Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.35,0:01:33.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.33,0:01:36.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類的帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.95,0:01:41.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白白的  好漂亮  像雪一般
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.56,0:01:46.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰都不撿嗎  那來我家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.03,0:01:52.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮  給媽媽看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.10,0:01:57.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.47,0:02:01.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  男子漢不能動不動就哭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.05,0:02:04.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後要獨自生活了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.89,0:02:15.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了  塔子阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.30,0:02:18.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心  玩得開心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.31,0:02:19.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.87,0:02:21.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴志
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.01,0:02:23.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.78,0:02:28.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為教學合宿要去雁羽溫泉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.42,0:02:30.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.09,0:02:36.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  要讓您出合宿的費用
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.03,0:02:40.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.27,0:02:43.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點事想拜託你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.01,0:02:49.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能到溫泉附近的窯戶去幫我取茶碗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.49,0:02:53.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來聯絡說是馬上就能做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.95,0:02:56.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能拜託你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.48,0:03:00.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了  滋叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.35,0:03:08.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑得真嚇人  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.65,0:03:14.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師  你什麼時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.10,0:03:18.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保鏢跟去是理所當然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.47,0:03:19.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.99,0:03:24.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這麼高興
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.51,0:03:31.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受人所托去做事  當然是很高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.63,0:03:50.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「強梁霸道終殄滅  恰似風前塵土揚」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.29,0:03:56.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  上午的課就上到這裏  午飯前是自由活動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.58,0:04:02.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  接下來去幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.57,0:04:04.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然先去泡溫泉啦  溫泉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.87,0:04:05.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.03,0:04:09.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我還有點重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.15,0:04:12.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.60,0:04:19.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.78,0:04:22.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概就在附近了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.91,0:04:25.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.31,0:04:33.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,膽小鬼小狐貍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.52,0:04:42.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在森林亂竄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.13,0:04:45.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廢物很礙眼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.09,0:04:54.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快滾出森林  廢物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.95,0:04:57.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廢物？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.40,0:04:59.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫你滾出去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.98,0:05:02.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.35,0:05:08.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.20,0:05:13.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幹什麼  欺負這麼小的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.65,0:05:17.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是人類嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.44,0:05:21.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類竟敢小看我們  不知天高地厚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.18,0:05:24.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我吃了你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.33,0:05:53.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.62,0:06:02.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是一樣愛管閒事啊  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.87,0:06:05.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.99,0:06:11.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這次可算是白來了  還得再過來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.76,0:06:16.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法嘛  茶碗要明天才能做好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.57,0:06:20.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類真是麻煩的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.68,0:06:26.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過是放食物的容器  在附近的超市買就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.89,0:06:29.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說就太直截了當了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.59,0:06:31.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體不是容器吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.53,0:06:32.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.20,0:06:33.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭人類
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.41,0:06:33.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是容器嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.41,0:06:34.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\an8\fad(0,300)}（註：貓咪老師把俗語作字面理解了,「沒有身體和蓋子」）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.85,0:06:34.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.34,0:06:37.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  要過去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.13,0:06:38.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了  來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.25,0:06:40.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.56,0:06:47.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  別睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.89,0:06:54.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.36,0:07:10.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才我被丟向夏目的粉筆打中了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.79,0:07:13.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.93,0:07:18.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚飯會是什麼呢  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.49,0:07:20.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  真期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.18,0:07:25.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目總是笑著  但總覺得不真實
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.88,0:07:32.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,語言和姿勢  連氣息…也覺得不真實
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.44,0:07:45.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許他並不是人類
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.17,0:07:52.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是跟我一樣化為人形獨自生活
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.24,0:07:57.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話  跟我一起住在這森林就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.05,0:08:00.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧  母親大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.72,0:08:17.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭疼了  明天就要回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.61,0:08:19.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過於親近的話他就太可憐了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.26,0:08:21.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.20,0:08:24.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了  老師
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.00,0:09:03.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真倒霉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.50,0:09:06.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣根本沒法去取茶碗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.23,0:09:09.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上課前能不能趕回去都是問題
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.10,0:09:13.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.33,0:09:19.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽錯了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.50,0:09:45.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.15,0:10:02.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親大人  我也能幫助別人了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.83,0:10:04.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他跟我說「謝謝你了」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.97,0:10:07.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不是沒用的人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.56,0:10:12.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天去摘蘑菇  摘很多很多  分給夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.20,0:10:20.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲  小狐貍  你還賴在這裏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.90,0:10:23.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不長記性的傢伙  說了叫你滾的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.43,0:10:36.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這森林不需要你這種廢物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.74,0:10:40.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  我不再是廢物了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.78,0:10:43.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裏不是…好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.18,0:10:43.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.44,0:10:50.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡的小子  不可原諒…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.16,0:10:58.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說過叫你們住手的了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.79,0:10:59.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.92,0:11:03.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.35,0:11:09.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只用拳頭還不夠嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.56,0:11:12.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目大人  夏目大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.47,0:11:14.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.69,0:11:17.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您忘記了嗎  夏目玲子大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.20,0:11:23.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說過到春天就將名字還給我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.08,0:11:27.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡的玲子  又幹這種罪孽深重的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.25,0:11:29.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春天？這是第幾個春天了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.01,0:11:35.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我的就是你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.19,0:11:38.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師  茶碗拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.43,0:11:48.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收下吧 早蕨 這是你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.55,0:11:56.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.16,0:11:59.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個友人帳的主人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.62,0:12:03.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我確實收到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.85,0:12:08.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友人帳？我聽說過
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.08,0:12:12.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被寫下名字的就會以主僕之契建立關係
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.83,0:12:15.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會被奪走名字的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.52,0:12:18.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.73,0:12:20.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.94,0:12:25.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛才歸還了名字  怎麼會去奪取名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.89,0:12:31.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫了我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.39,0:12:33.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓我做你的手下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.05,0:12:35.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會起到作用的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.40,0:12:38.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.91,0:12:47.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我很軟弱嗎  我沒用嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.12,0:12:51.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想用這種東西來互相束縛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.55,0:12:55.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不是主人跟手下的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.50,0:12:58.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.54,0:13:04.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得我們擁有其他的羈絆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.16,0:13:18.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顏色真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.32,0:13:20.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去換衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.59,0:13:24.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友介紹給我一處好窯戶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.13,0:13:28.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為家族增加了  就藉機訂一套
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.52,0:13:34.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你的份  貴志
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.68,0:13:37.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝您了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.88,0:13:41.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像小狐貍說的那樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.83,0:13:43.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.29,0:13:46.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是有沒有用的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.86,0:13:49.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  完全不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.78,0:13:59.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.92,0:14:04.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想給夏目也看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.03,0:14:09.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目…我想見夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.29,0:14:15.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男子漢不能動不動就哭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.90,0:14:19.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我決定要變強  總有一天能幫上夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.09,0:14:26.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼想見夏目嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.62,0:14:29.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽過傳言了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.11,0:14:35.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像認識那個擁有友人帳的夏目嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.17,0:14:40.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不能完全化作人類嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.64,0:14:42.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.56,0:14:50.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能讓我吃魚吃個飽  就告訴你能跟夏目見面的方法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.37,0:15:15.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣…你能告訴我跟夏目見面的方法了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.72,0:15:24.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨狐貍  你被騙了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.33,0:15:28.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因為你這麼笨  才會總是孤單一人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.33,0:15:32.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目早就忘記你了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.37,0:15:40.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收下吧  小狐貍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.45,0:15:44.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能變成人類一天的藥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.86,0:15:47.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變成人類的藥？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.27,0:15:52.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想見面只要自己去見就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.70,0:15:54.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這麼簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.24,0:16:01.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  只要去見他就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.59,0:16:27.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  我好歹也是狐貍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.31,0:16:31.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要去人類的世界  就能追尋夏目的氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.78,0:16:34.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了  母親大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.21,0:16:57.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目一個人有沒有寂寞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.93,0:17:15.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目的氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.92,0:17:30.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  夏目的氣味…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.62,0:17:45.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想見他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.32,0:17:51.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  你在哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.26,0:17:54.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.00,0:17:58.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  你沒事吧  一個人嗎  媽媽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.51,0:17:59.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一個人沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.47,0:18:07.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想見他  好想見他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.82,0:18:09.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裏  夏目在哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.11,0:18:12.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.81,0:18:15.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上鉤了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.57,0:18:16.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快啦  快啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.47,0:18:18.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.19,0:18:20.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是夏目啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.87,0:18:21.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大豐收嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.25,0:18:23.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.09,0:18:29.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼在吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.72,0:18:37.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目的氣味  在這裏  就在這附近
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.01,0:18:38.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能見面了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.72,0:19:08.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好了哦  貴志釣的真鱒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.97,0:19:12.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是條好真鱒  開動了  貴志
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.60,0:19:13.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.68,0:19:15.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴志能吃河魚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.13,0:19:17.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我都能吃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.21,0:19:20.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不吃的東西要說出來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.69,0:19:25.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滋他不吃青椒  像小孩子一樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.53,0:19:29.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我小時候也不吃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.37,0:19:32.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  有同伴了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.65,0:19:36.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.11,0:19:43.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔子  這真鱒非常好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.02,0:19:46.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也嘗一口吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.56,0:19:47.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請吧請吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.99,0:19:49.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.97,0:19:56.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  很好吃  能吃到這麼美味的東西真開心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.20,0:20:07.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  夏目看起來很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.20,0:20:09.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.27,0:20:15.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寂寞的…寂寞的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.61,0:20:24.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.74,0:20:32.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.95,0:20:35.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是那時的小狐貍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.55,0:20:39.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  特地來見我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.91,0:21:17.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛的帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.08,0:21:20.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃完飯一起回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.38,0:21:27.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得記住路啊  下次我去見你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.61,0:21:32.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.76,0:21:43.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.83,0:21:49.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就算寂寞也不敢邁出腳步  沒想過去做點什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.98,0:21:55.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以或許很多東西就無法察覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.07,0:23:51.09,biaoti1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(140,550)}虛幻之光
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.75,0:23:38.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人能看見妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.73,0:23:41.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與之交心  終於成為了重要的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.73,0:23:42.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.57,0:23:44.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變得無法看見妖怪了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.79,0:23:47.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那個人能幸福  我就沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.15,0:23:50.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎  清
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,

